data.description: Introducing this charming 2-bed, 1.5-bath condo nestled in the desirable Fox Ridge development on the West Side of Indianapolis. Key features include a fireplace, vaulted ceilings, quiet surroundings and easy access to all that Indianapolis has to offer. Situated just moments away from the stunning Eagle Creek Park, the world-renowned Indianapolis Motor Speedway, the bustling heart of downtown Brownsburg, and a mere 18-minute drive from the convenience of Indianapolis International Airport, this condo offers an ideal location for those seeking an active and accessible lifestyle.
